AUDIO: 'Introducing SwitchX. SwitchX is our new&nbsp; video-to-video model that lets you change&nbsp;&nbsp; your background and lighting in a single click&nbsp; while keeping the subject\'s detail exactly the&nbsp;&nbsp; same. Build yourself a professional podcast&nbsp; studio or go to the streets of New York. Go&nbsp;&nbsp; anywhere with same you but a different world.&nbsp; You don\'t have to wait for the perfect lights,&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[00:17] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'perfect locations, or perfect time of the day&nbsp; to shoot your perfect content. Anywhere can&nbsp;&nbsp; be your perfect studio. Here\'s how it works.&nbsp; Upload your video and select the subject that&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[00:29] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'you want to keep. Then create a reference&nbsp; image to define the lighting, background,&nbsp;&nbsp; and mood. Even if the subject looks different a&nbsp; bit, SwitchX will automatically fix it. And it\'s&nbsp;&nbsp; not just changing background. You can actually&nbsp; relight the entire scene or change your clothes&nbsp;&nbsp;'

[00:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'depending on how you provide a mask. SwitchX&nbsp; is available for free during the beta period&nbsp;&nbsp; at Beeble. come to Beeble and try it out.&nbsp; I\'d love to hear what you guys think. Thank&nbsp;&nbsp; you. What do you think about SwitchX? It\'s&nbsp; damn awesome. You should try it right now.'
